    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="ag-x3D-do-act"><a href="#ag-x3D-do-act" class="headerlink" title="ag&#x3D;do,act"></a>ag&#x3D;do,act</h1><p>Ag<strong>ent</strong>(表人)  代理人<br>Agent<strong>ial</strong>(形容词)  代理人的<br>Ag<strong>ency</strong>(表性质)  机构<br>Agen<strong>da</strong>  议事日程</p><h1 id="Agri-x3D-field-土地"><a href="#Agri-x3D-field-土地" class="headerlink" title="Agri&#x3D;field(土地)"></a>Agri&#x3D;field(土地)</h1><p><strong>agri</strong>culture  农业<br>agricultur<strong>al</strong>  农业的<br><strong>Agr</strong>onomy  农学的<br>Agronom<strong>ist</strong>  农学家<br>Agrarian 土地的</p><h1 id="Ann-x3D-year"><a href="#Ann-x3D-year" class="headerlink" title="Ann&#x3D;year"></a>Ann&#x3D;year</h1><p>Annual  年度的<br>Anni<strong>vers</strong>(转)ary  周年纪念日(一年转一次)<br><strong>Per</strong>(全部，自始自终)ennial  全年的<br><strong>Semi</strong>(一半)annual  半年一次的</p><h1 id="Audi-x3D-hear"><a href="#Audi-x3D-hear" class="headerlink" title="Audi&#x3D;hear"></a>Audi&#x3D;hear</h1><p>Audio  听觉的<br>Audi<strong>ence</strong>(表名词)  听众<br>Aud<strong>ible</strong>(能…的) 听得见的<br>Audit  旁听;审计(旁听公司流程)<br>Auditor  审计员<br>Audition  听觉<br>Audi-visual  试听法</p><h1 id="Bell-x3D-war-bell响铃，吹响战争号角"><a href="#Bell-x3D-war-bell响铃，吹响战争号角" class="headerlink" title="Bell&#x3D;war(bell响铃，吹响战争号角)"></a>Bell&#x3D;war(bell响铃，吹响战争号角)</h1><p><strong>Re</strong>(回，向后)bel  反叛(回过来打自己人)<br>Rebell<strong>ion</strong>  叛乱<br>Belliger<strong>ent</strong>(关于…的)  好战的</p><h1 id="Brev-x3D-short"><a href="#Brev-x3D-short" class="headerlink" title="Brev&#x3D;short"></a>Brev&#x3D;short</h1><p>Breif  简短的<br>Breviary  缩短，摘要<br>Brevity  简洁<br><strong>Ab</strong>(加强)breviate  缩短<br>Abbreviation  缩写</p><h1 id="cept-x3D-take-拿"><a href="#cept-x3D-take-拿" class="headerlink" title="cept&#x3D;take(拿)"></a>cept&#x3D;take(拿)</h1><p><strong>Ex</strong>(出)cept  除…之外(拿出去)<br>Exceptional  例外的<br>Exceptive  特殊的<br><strong>Ac</strong>(加强)cept  接受<br>Acception  承认<br><strong>Inter</strong>(在…中间)cept  拦截(在中间抓住)<br>Interception  截取<br>Incept  接受</p><h1 id="ced-x2F-ceed-x2F-cess-x3D-go"><a href="#ced-x2F-ceed-x2F-cess-x3D-go" class="headerlink" title="ced&#x2F;ceed&#x2F;cess&#x3D;go"></a>ced&#x2F;ceed&#x2F;cess&#x3D;go</h1><p><strong>Pre</strong>(在前的)cede  先行，领先(始终保持在前方的状态)<br>Preced<strong>ent</strong>(表名词) 先例(在前面的东西)<br>Precedent<strong>ed</strong>  有先例的<br><strong>Un</strong>precedented  空前的(没有先例)<br>Exceed  超出<br>Excess  超过<br>Excessive  过分的<br><strong>Pro</strong>ceed  前进，进行<br>Proced<strong>ure</strong>  程序，过程<br>Process  过程<br>Procession 队伍<br>Antecedent  先行词<br>Antecessor  先驱者，祖宗<br><strong>Suc</strong>(后)cessor  继承者<br>Successive  连续的<br><strong>Re</strong>(向后)cede  后退<br>Retrocede  后退<br><strong>Inter</strong>cede  调解（在两者之间不让走，调停）<br>Intercession  说情</p>]]></content>
    
    
